text: Pullach, officially Pullach i. Isartal, is a municipality in Munich in Bavaria in Germany. It is on the Isar Valley Railway and is served by the S 7 line of the Munich S-Bahn, at the Großhesselohe Isartalbahnhof, Pullach and Höllriegelskreuth railway stations. ==References== Category:Munich (district)
